RIZZO--Frank A. The Association of the Attending Staff of the Mount Sinai Hospital mourns the passing of our colleague, teacher, and friend. Dr. Rizzo devoted 40 years of service to the institution, specializing in Neurology and Neuro - Endocrinology. He was an excellent and extremely compassionate clinician and a very fine person. We will miss his energy and enthusiasm. Our sincere condolences to his family. Vicki Lopachin, M.D. -President Thomas McGinn, M.D. -Vice President Amy Weinstein -Administrator
